<li>The extended form will put an extended part of the article on an additional page, for long articles or articles with multiple pics.
<li>Use &lt;a href=*url* target="_whole"&gt;*Link Title*&lt;/a&gt; for links and put &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Source:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;a href=*url* target="_whole"&gt;*Link Title*&gt; after your post to link to your source if you got the information off the net - it will look and act like this when done correctly: <b>Source:</b> <a href=/sonichq/ target="whole">Sonic HQ</a>.
